CustomField.description: VERIFIED: Means the counts match RESCANNER: Means the type should be selected on the scanner page and rescanned. DEDUPLICATE: Means that the deduplicate tool should be run. NOT DETECTED: Means that no records of that type have been located.
CustomField.formula: IF( FLODocs__Scanner_Count__c = FLODocs__Total_Customization__c, "VERIFIED", IF(FLODocs__Scanner_Count__c < FLODocs__Total_Customization__c,"RESCANNER", IF(FLODocs__Scanner_Count__c > FLODocs__Total_Customization__c,"DEDUPLICATE","NOT DETECTED")))
CustomField.inlineHelpText: VERIFIED: Means the counts match RESCANNER: Means the type should be selected on the scanner page and rescanned. DEDUPLICATE: Means that the deduplicate tool should be run. NOT DETECTED: Means that no records of that type have been located.
CustomField.label: Retrieved Stage
